      "title": "I.O.C. Further lowers the fuel limit",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Indian Oil (IOC) has reduced the supply limit at petrol stations.",
        "Accordingly, the I.O.C. Fuel stations charge Rs. 1,500 for a motorcycle, Rs. 2,500 for a three-wheeler and Rs. 7,000 for other vehicles at a time, the company said.",
        "Previously I.O.C. At petrol stations he issued at a time Rs. 2,500 for a motorcycle, Rs. 3,000 for a three-wheeler and Rs. 10,000 for other vehicles."
      ],
